Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Earth, seventy million years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were sent here by a time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii has looked for Okarin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in many, many, many world lines, chasing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that the Okarin here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of many Okarins. \NAnd you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's the original Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you could also say the Mayushii here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of many Mayushiis. \NAnd you could say that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she's the original, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Okarin and Mayushii are gonna die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that our wills will carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.23,0:01:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Okarin and Mayushii, in Akihabara, \Nseventy million years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:17.31,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogma in Ergosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan says to come in, \Nbecause she's almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mayushii's cosplay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could hold this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Keep it spread out like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ribbon's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have some cosplay outfits for Comima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cosplay, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interested?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wear this around others...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.53,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a time leap machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.76,0:04:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like an evil organization's \Nbrainwashing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like Phone Microwave-chan, \Nnow with headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not look like much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but theoretically, this can transmit \Nmemories into the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially now that we can use the LHC.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The LHC's involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's basically a problem of compression.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.99,Sign12A,,0000,0000,0000,,Me on 2010/8/13 AD                    Hippocampus
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this machine reads the signals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,comprising memories in the brain, \Nencoding them as data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:45.93,Sign12A,,0000,0000,0000,,Scan Memory Data (3.24T)\NNerve Pulse Signals  -->  Encode to Electric Signals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In total, it's 3.24 terabytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Phone Microwave
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.12,Sign12B,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Leap Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:53.22,Sign12B,,0000,0000,0000,,Generate a black hole with the LHC
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.94,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can only send a little over 36 bytes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, data at the terabyte level \Nis out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we send it to the LHC,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:57.68,Sign12B,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN \NTime leap machine \NUse the black hole with the data \N\NCompress!         3.24 T --> 36 byte
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,use the black hole to compress it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then send it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.47,Sign12C,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Leap Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.35,Sign12B,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Leap! \N(Same as D-Mail)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:02.93,Sign12A,,0000,0000,0000,,Me on 2010/8/11 AD \NOverwrite Memory Data!      Receive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using the same method as the D-mail \Nto send it to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like putting a futon that won't fit in a \Ncloset inside a compression bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strictly speaking, it's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's close enough for you to get an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as with the D-mail, \Nwe can send data to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we use the cell phone's \Nspread spectrum waves to copy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the future memories to the brain in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This creates a "you" with memories from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The furthest back you can send data \Nis forty-eight hours at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any further, and the two brain states'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,difference is too large,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it might fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's one other problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the Phone Microwave or the D-mail,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need an experiment subject,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or we can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're sending memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only way to know if it succeeded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to use a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:06:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, one of us has to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.35,0:06:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe, tell me what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.74,0:06:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Hououin... Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Sup?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know why the line connected to SERN, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.99,0:06:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's nothing to indicate\Nthe hacking has been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they'd really noticed, \Nthey would have done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.60,0:06:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really overcome time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part of me wants to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't Mayushii buy some bananas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can time leap the\Nbananas that Mayushii bought
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, I explained, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bananas have no memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we won't do the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll announce this to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give the time leap machine \Nto an appropriate organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're okay with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii really agrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida ordered pizza, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just make the salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll need...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said salad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, grapefruit salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do we have natto \Nand ground beef in the cart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can make some good stuff by combining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The grapefruit is sour, so you can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,combine anything with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see, once you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want salad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a complete salad right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's 50% off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun buying something that's already made.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why guys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only interested in experiments are no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.06,0:07:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here's the coriander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Organization's agent has finally made her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:07:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a cat just out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face says, "I'm free at last!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected you to say we were starting
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the time leap experiment immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dissatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On a fundamental level, \Nhumans are temporal creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heidegger said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I was relieved when you said \Nwe wouldn't do the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone else agrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, if we're having a party,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}can I call Ruka-chan and Feyris-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a development conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri might have been thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should stop, for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she may have seen \Nmore than the two of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we've been obsessed with the experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do we announce it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sooner the better, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to contact my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad will also find out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I made a time leap machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we won't be able to go to Aomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll solve my lab members' problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to abuse me as your assistant, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my dear companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might have a fever
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you're saying un-assistant-like things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just being polite...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tsundere is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a tsundere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always, always say the craziest stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and now you're talking about companions?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lab members are my allies,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the world my enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stunned, I can't speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to trip me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snacking while everyone's out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pizza doesn't taste good cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, why are all three of them the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My personal taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can be so dictatorial?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to buy the ingredients, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second. I'll get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did! With all my might! With all I had!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, you said you'd protect \Nyour lab members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might not be over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still possible
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the apple pie was just a failed attempt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and normally...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot radishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess sweet pickles will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this meal is over, \NI'm going to retire and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri, I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the kitchen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I smell something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pizza's here already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my kara-age...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Makise Kurisu here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm a lab member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.38,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a lab member.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan, did something happen \Nbetween you and Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just keeps blaming me for the craziest stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I'm a SERN spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crazy. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know more about you than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you really are,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what you're going to do after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes so little sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurisu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back, Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Hououin Kyouma can handle this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I raised you better than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't raise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you what the most important thing \Nis about being a mad scientist...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not listening, and I won't be a mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I warned Okabe Rintaro, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beware of Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you believed her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't tell me I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you making things worse?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't like fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't really like it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're all together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be more fun if we were friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consider well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.44,0:13:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that card a link?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Part-time soldier, your fate as a soldier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the last slice of cake, rests on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When in doubt, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my motto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you have three viruses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me you give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll give you the cherry on top.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane is taking this too seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.30,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin, you're being mean to Suzu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the world of games, it's live or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I was raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones lined up in the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are definitely link cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Okabe's personality, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my assistant, yet you betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that arrogance of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I won't thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii will help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you get tea for everyone, Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.13,0:14:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kurisu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii is happy you \Nmade friends with Suzu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not really friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we're all together, it's more fun to get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking with Okabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the clearest view of the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only time Okabe's looked serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean to Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, part-time warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won, but not of your own ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so arrogant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off to plan for round two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy it while you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last dessert of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go check on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:15:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't find a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cyalume Saber is Future Gadget #6.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use it as a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pizza was good,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Suzu-san and Kurisu-chan were having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we've got lots of lab members now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking that lately, \Nwe've been lacking a bunch of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.15,0:16:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, chairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we need more utensils...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait just a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.34,0:17:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we announce we've made a time leap machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll get some kind of reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will solve everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can buy chairs and utensils?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I said we could buy those \Nand still have money left over?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a microwave, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss being able to heat up my kara-age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked really lonely in the spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lab was always quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could hear was the sound of your computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now there's Daru-kun and Kurisu-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ruka-chan, Suzu-san, Moeka-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feyris-chan, and Mr. Braun and Nae-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Mayushii isn't your hostage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin! Mayushii!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trains stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:23.31,Sign12D,,0000,0000,0000,,Bomb threat? \NAkihabara in panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For those of you just tuning in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the following lines have been shut down, \Ndue to a bomb threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamanote Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soubu Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb threat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This party was to celebrate the \Ntime leap machine's completion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why mention that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still hacking into SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say that. I got in deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a direct connection to SERN.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.76,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! You need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Mayushii?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a taxi home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Don't have the money for a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wound it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.67,0:20:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have been suspended...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, put your hands up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moeka-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiryuu Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN will take the time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SERN?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe Rintaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hashida Itaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You three are coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mayuri is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For FB... FB... FB...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
